---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@graph": [
    {
      "@type": "WebPage",
      "@id": "https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz/website-copywriting-auckland/",
      "url": "https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz/website-copywriting-auckland/",
      "name": "Website Copywriting",
      "description": "Clear and effective website copywriting for small businesses in Auckland. Improve conversions with practical content that fits your brand.",
      "inLanguage": "en-NZ",
      "isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz/#website"
      },
      "breadcrumb": {
        "@id": "https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz/website-copywriting-auckland/#breadcrumb"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
      "@id": "https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz/website-copywriting-auckland/#breadcrumb",
      "itemListElement": [
        {
          "@type": "ListItem",
          "position": 1,
          "name": "Home",
          "item": "https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz/"
        },
        {
          "@type": "ListItem",
          "position": 2,
          "name": "Website Copywriting"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "@id": "https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz/#organization",
      "name": "Kiwi Web Design",
      "url": "https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz",
      "logo": {
        "@type": "ImageObject",
        "url": "https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/android-chrome-512x512-1.png"
      }
    }
  ]
};
---
<Layout title="Website Copywriting" description="Clear and effective website copywriting for small businesses in Auckland. Improve conversions with practical content that fits your brand." schema={schema}>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">Website Services</p>
        <h1>Website Copywriting Services for Auckland Businesses</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Clear and effective website copywriting for small businesses in Auckland. Improve conversions with practical content that fits your brand.</p>
        <div class="hero-btns">
          <a href="/website-designer-auckland/#contact" class="btn-primary">Book Free Consultation</a>
          <a href="/small-business-website-design-auckland/#packages" class="btn-outline">View Packages</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-img">
        <img src="https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/website-copywriting-auckland-kiwiwebdesign.jpg" alt="Website Copywriting Services for Auckland Businesses" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="prose">
<img src="https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/website-copywriting-auckland-kiwiwebdesign.jpg" alt="Website copywriting services for Auckland businesses" loading="lazy"> 


 <p>Your website design is only as strong as the words on the page. If visitors cannot quickly understand what you do, who you help, and what to do next, they leave.</p>
 <p>We write practical website copy for small businesses in Auckland and across New Zealand. The focus is clear messaging, simple structure, and calls to action that match how real customers make decisions.</p>
 <p>This service fits well with our <a href="/">web design Auckland</a> and <a href="/">website design Auckland</a> projects, or as a standalone copy refresh for an existing site.</p>


    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="faq-inner">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>SEO Focused Content</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>We write copy that supports the keywords you are targeting in Google and AI search, without making the content feel forced or robotic.</p>
 <p>Includes:</p>
 <ul>
 <li>Page level keyword focus</li>
 <li>Supporting headings and subheadings</li>
 <li>Local references to Auckland and your suburbs</li>
 <li>On-page suggestions for internal links and CTAs</li>
 </ul></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Content Refresh & Clean Up</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>If you already have a website, we can improve what is there instead of starting again. This suits businesses that feel their site is “OK” but not clear enough.</p>
 <p>Includes:</p>
 <ul>
 <li>Review of existing pages</li>
 <li>Rewrite or tighten key sections</li>
 <li>Align tone and structure across the site</li>
 <li>Suggestions for new content gaps</li>
 </ul></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Microcopy & Calls To Action</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Short lines such as button labels, form headings, and small notes often make the difference between someone enquiring or dropping off.</p>
 <p>Includes:</p>
 <ul>
 <li>Button copy and form instructions</li>
 <li>Short reassurance messages near forms</li>
 <li>Contact and booking prompts</li>
 </ul></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How The Copywriting Process Works</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>The process is simple and structured so you know what is happening at each step. We can work alongside a new build, a redesign, or an existing WordPress or Shopify site.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>1. Discovery Call</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>We start with a short call to understand your business, services, ideal customers, and any current website issues.</p>
 <p>We cover:</p>
 <ul>
 <li>What is working and not working now</li>
 <li>Your goals for the next 6 to 12 months</li>
 <li>Your main services and locations</li>
 </ul></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>2. Content Plan & Page Outline</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>You receive a simple content plan that lists each page, the purpose of the page, and the key sections we will write.</p>
 <p>This helps you see:</p>
 <ul>
 <li>Which pages are essential for launch</li>
 <li>What can be added later as “Phase 2” content</li>
 <li>How users will move through the site</li>
 </ul></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>3. Draft Copy & Review</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>We write the first draft and send it in a clear format that is easy to comment on. You can request changes where needed.</p>
 <p>Most clients:</p>
 <ul>
 <li>Adjust a few phrases to match how they speak</li>
 <li>Add details about services or pricing</li>
 <li>Clarify anything that customers often ask</li>
 </ul></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>4. Final Copy & Hand Over</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>We finalise the content after revisions and prepare it so you or your developer can add it to the website without confusion.</p>
 <p>Depending on the project, we can:</p>
 <ul>
 <li>Provide copy in a shared document with clear page labels</li>
 <li>Match copy directly to your WordPress layout or template</li>
 <li>Coordinate with your developer or designer if needed</li>
 </ul></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What We Need From You</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Copywriting works best when we have basic information at the start. You do not need perfectly written notes. Bullet points are fine.</p>
 <ul>
 <li>List of services and main locations you serve</li>
 <li>Any current brochures, proposals, or emails you already use</li>
 <li>Clarity on your preferred enquiry type: phone, form, booking, or email</li>
 <li>Any competitors you like or dislike and why</li>
 </ul>

<p>If you are planning a new website or feel your current content is holding you back, professional copywriting will help you convert more of your existing traffic.</p>
 <p>Talk to us about website copywriting or a full website project today.</p>
 <p>
 <a href="/website-designer-auckland/">
 Contact Kiwi Web Design
 </a>
 </p></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Website Copywriting FAQs</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><details>
 <summary>How long does website copywriting take?</summary>
 <p>For a standard small business website of 4 to 6 main pages, most projects take three to seven working days once we have all the information from you. More complex sites, such as multi service or multi location websites, can take longer and we will outline timeframes before we start.</p>
 </details>

 <details>
 <summary>Do you research and use SEO keywords?</summary>
 <p>Yes. We work with your existing SEO plan or help you choose realistic target phrases for Auckland and New Zealand. The copy is written in natural language so it reads well for humans while still supporting SEO and future AI search.</p>
 </details>

 <details>
 <summary>Can you rewrite my current website content?</summary>
 <p>Yes. Many clients come to us with a site that is live but not performing. We review your existing pages, keep what is still useful, remove what is confusing or repetitive, and rewrite the key sections so the message is clearer for your ideal customer.</p>
 </details>

 <details>
 <summary>Do I have to be in Auckland to work with you?</summary>
 <p>No. We work mainly with Auckland businesses, but also support clients across New Zealand using Zoom, phone, and email. The process is the same, and we tailor the content to your local region or service areas.</p>
 </details>

 <details>
 <summary>Can you also help with website design and build?</summary>
 <p>Yes. Website copywriting is available as a standalone service or as part of a full website project with Kiwi Web Design. If you prefer the complete package, we handle planning, <a href="/">web design Auckland</a>, build, and content so you have a single point of contact.</p>
 </details>

 <details>
 <summary>How do we start?</summary>
 <p>Send us a message with a short description of your business and your current website situation. We will suggest a simple scope of work and next steps.</p>
 </details>

<!-- FAQ Schema --></div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="cta-strip">
    <h2>Ready to grow your business online?</h2>
    <p>Let's build something that works for you. Free consultation, no obligation.</p>
    <div class="cta-btns">
      <a href="/website-designer-auckland/#contact" class="btn-primary">Book Free Consultation</a>
      <a href="/small-business-website-design-auckland/#packages" class="btn-outline">View Our Packages</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ── hero ── */
  .hero { background: var(--kwd-dark); color: var(--kwd-white); padding: 4rem 0 3rem; }
  .hero-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; display: flex; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; }
  .hero-text { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .eyebrow { font-size: .75rem; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--kwd-yellow); font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .6rem; }
  .hero-text h1 { font-family: var(--kwd-font-heading); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); margin: 0 0 1rem; line-height: 1.2; }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 1.05rem; opacity: .85; max-width: 580px; margin: 0 0 2rem; line-height: 1.65; }
  .hero-btns { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .75rem; }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--kwd-yellow); color: var(--kwd-dark); padding: .75rem 1.75rem; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; font-size: .95rem; }
  .btn-outline { border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.6); color: var(--kwd-white); padding: .75rem 1.75rem; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; font-size: .95rem; }
  .hero-img { flex: 0 0 42%; }
  .hero-img img { width: 100%; border-radius: 10px; object-fit: cover; max-height: 380px; display: block; }
  /* ── prose content ── */
  .page-content { padding: 3.5rem 0; }
  .prose { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .prose h1 { font-family: var(--kwd-font-heading); font-size: 2rem; margin: 0 0 1rem; color: var(--kwd-dark); }
  .prose h2 { font-family: var(--kwd-font-heading); font-size: 1.6rem; margin: 2.5rem 0 .75rem; color: var(--kwd-dark); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--kwd-yellow); padding-bottom: .3rem; }
  .prose h3 { font-family: var(--kwd-font-heading); font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 1.75rem 0 .5rem; color: var(--kwd-dark); }
  .prose h4 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 1.25rem 0 .4rem; color: #222; }
  .prose h5, .prose h6 { font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 1rem 0 .35rem; color: #333; }
  .prose p { margin: 0 0 1rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #333; }
  .prose ul { padding-left: 1.4rem; margin: 0 0 1rem; list-style: disc; }
  .prose ol { padding-left: 1.4rem; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  .prose li { margin-bottom: .4rem; line-height: 1.65; color: #333; }
  .prose img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px; margin: 1.75rem 0; display: block; }
  .prose blockquote { border-left: 4px solid var(--kwd-yellow); padding: .75rem 1.25rem; margin: 1.75rem 0; background: #f8f6f0; font-style: italic; color: #444; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; }
  .prose a { color: var(--kwd-dark); text-decoration: underline; font-weight: 600; }
  .prose a:hover { color: var(--kwd-brown); }
  .prose strong { color: var(--kwd-dark); }
  .prose table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1.75rem 0; font-size: .9rem; overflow-x: auto; display: block; }
  .prose th, .prose td { padding: .65rem 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: left; white-space: nowrap; }
  .prose th { background: var(--kwd-dark); color: var(--kwd-white); }
  .prose tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #fafafa; }
  /* ── faq ── */
  .faq-section { background: var(--kwd-cream); padding: 4rem 0; }
  .faq-inner { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .faq-inner > h2 { font-family: var(--kwd-font-heading); font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 0 0 2rem; color: var(--kwd-dark); }
  .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid #d8d0c0; }
  .faq-item summary { cursor: pointer; padding: 1.1rem 0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; color: var(--kwd-dark); }
  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .faq-item summary::after { content: '+'; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--kwd-yellow); flex-shrink: 0; margin-left: .75rem; }
  .faq-item[open] summary::after { content: '−'; }
  .faq-answer { padding: .25rem 0 1.25rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #444; }
  .faq-answer p { margin: 0 0 .6rem; }
  .faq-answer ul, .faq-answer ol { padding-left: 1.3rem; margin: 0 0 .6rem; }
  /* ── cta ── */
  .cta-strip { background: var(--kwd-dark); color: var(--kwd-white); text-align: center; padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
  .cta-strip h2 { font-family: var(--kwd-font-heading); font-size: 2rem; margin: 0 0 .75rem; }
  .cta-strip p { opacity: .85; margin: 0 0 2rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .cta-btns { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .75rem; justify-content: center; }
  /* ── contact form ── */
  .contact-section { padding: 4rem 0; background: var(--kwd-cream); }
  .contact-inner { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .contact-inner h2 { font-family: var(--kwd-font-heading); font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 0 0 .5rem; color: var(--kwd-dark); }
  .contact-inner > p { margin: 0 0 2rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.65; }
  .contact-form { display: grid; gap: 1.25rem; }
  .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .4rem; }
  .form-group label { font-weight: 600; font-size: .9rem; color: var(--kwd-dark); }
  .form-group input, .form-group textarea, .form-group select { padding: .7rem 1rem; border: 2px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-family: inherit; background: #fff; transition: border-color .2s; }
  .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--kwd-yellow); }
  .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 130px; }
  .form-submit { margin-top: .5rem; }
  /* ── responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-inner { flex-direction: column; }
    .hero-img { display: none; }
    .hero-text h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; }
  }
</style>
